    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You my friend may have ingested some weird thing on your desk and now you are dreaming some.. Questionable?. . . dreams? If you do not wake up in time you may never wake up again and if you die in your dreams so will you die in real life too. Protect yourself with various weapons made by YOU from YOU. Like this beautiful pistol constructed from your uhhh.. foreskin? you needed a new cut anyways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035890/extras/7a68480e7c99aba0ecc200c8b2d028f0.poster.avif?t=1758214885\" width=618 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035890/extras/7a68480e7c99aba0ecc200c8b2d028f0.webm?t=1758214885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>A beauty isn’t it? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With that out of the way. Explore more of the deepest depths of your wildest imagination in first person. Fill up your inventory with various items and weapons you can find and shoot everything that stands in your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035890/extras/eb32b269129bce61e2dbe338e189cccd.poster.avif?t=1758214885\" width=420 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035890/extras/eb32b269129bce61e2dbe338e189cccd.webm?t=1758214885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035890/extras/eb32b269129bce61e2dbe338e189cccd.mp4?t=1758214885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ohhhhhh yea. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fentanyl Edition is a Fast-Paced Arena Shooter It puts you against many horrifyingly bizarre entities that are created from the deepest depths of your imagination you have 2 hands to fight with and an arsenal of items varying from Guns to foreskin. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DESCLAIMER: short game :)</p>",
